104
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,760
and mobilize the troops to the palace.

105
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,480
Okay.

106
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,040
Remember,

107
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,360
