111
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,520
You die,

112
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,520
I die with you.

113
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,920
Outrageous!

114
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,080
How dare you

115
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,840
treat me like this!

116
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,560
Even if Cang Hanyu isn't dead, so what?

117
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,720
You're already surrounded.

118
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:51,520
Even if the gods come down,
they can't save you.

119
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,480
Do you hear the hoofbeats?

120
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,960
The reinforcements of Donglan
will be here soon.

121
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,840
Let's see who wins in the end.

122
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:04,760
Ya!

123
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:16,380
(Yingrui)

124
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:31,160
I don't want to listen to your foolish talk.

125
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,840
Give me the Phoenix Hairpin

126
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,080
